Title : Shinga, Democratic Republic of the Congo
Text : '''Shinga''' is a village in the [[Katanga Province]] of the [[Democratic Republic of the Congo]].<ref>{{GEOnet2|32FA8823CD743774E0440003BA962ED3|Shinga (Approved)}}, [[National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency|United States National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency]]</ref>  It lies at an elevation of 913 meters near the Mulombotwa River. It is about 30 kilometers by road southeast of the railhead and town of [[Kabongo, Democratic Republic of the Congo|Kabongo]].<ref>{{Cite map|title=SB 35-14, Kabongo, Zaire|scale=1:250,000|date=June 1979|publisher=Defense Mapping Agency|url=http://www.lib.utexas.edu/maps/jog/central_africa/sb-35-7-kongolo-zaire.pdf}}</ref>

